cdata.name: Blockvest
cdata.desc:
Based in the U.S.A, Blockvestis a decentralized payment platform. It gives users the tools to manage their digital assets through services such as a digital wallet namedNvestnode Wallet, which allows users to safeguard and monitor their cryptocurrencies, and an Exchange platform soinvestors can trade (buy/sell) digital assets 24/7 in a decentralized manner. Inan attempt to solve de volatility problem,BlockvestBLV Tokens holders will be able to earn a secondary Stablecoin denominated in US dollars called Yield (YLD), which value is locked on 1 USD. Yieldholders will pay fees to the users who perform transactions on the platform.

The BLV token is an Ethereum-based ERC20 cryptocurrency. It's the security token created and developed by Blockvestto power the platform. In addition, the BLV token is supported by theBlockvest features (digital wallet, crypto Exchange).
